OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FArtist's delight as book   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbecomes BBC film           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The author and illustrator of a book   
OL,6, that has been turned into a short film 
OL,7, to be broadcast on BBC One later has   
OL,8, described the experience as "surreal". 
OL,10,FCharlie Mackesy's The Boy, the Mole,   
OL,11,Fthe Fox and the Horse will be aired at 
OL,12,F16:55 GMT and available on iPlayer     
OL,13,Fshortly afterwards.                    
OL,15,FMr Mackesy said he spent two years     
OL,16,Fworking on the film in Suffolk, where  
OL,17,Fhis family live.                       
OL,19,FHe said it was "a thrill" to see his   
OL,20,Fcharacters moving on film.             
